title: TRAVEL: Delays on East Coast Main Line
text:
Credit: Credit: David Parry/PA Archive/PA Images There are currently 90 minute delays to rail services on the East Coast Main Line. This is due to an obstruction on the line between Alnmouth and Morpeth.
Delays are expected until 10.00am.
